{
  "stem": "33.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we didn't know, because they didn't know, that actually these camps are death camps-- that people are being systematically murdered.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We assumed, and we knew, that people die at a higher rate than in normal life, but we thought that that's due to malnutrition, lack of medical attention, inadequate shelter, and such.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had absolutely no idea that people are being murdered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We heard about early concentration camps like Dachau or Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we never even heard about Auschwitz or any of the camps in Poland, or occupied Poland, as it may be.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In the 1940's, even though terrible things were going on, but partially because we didn't know how terrible they were, and also when you're 14, 15, 16, you pretty much have your own life.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was still a happy go lucky teenager.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had my home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had loving parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had friends.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had a school that I went to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So my life was just as normal as any other teenager's.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I went ice skating in the winter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I went down to the river; to the beach in the summer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We started to-- not really belong-- but have some activities-- Jewish related.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Like, for instance, there was the young WIZO-- W-I-Z-O.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I think it's probably Women's Zionist Organization-- something like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we had-- like people had done plays, and we had recitals and certain activities.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Also, we-- this was probably by 1942, '43-- through our Sunday school teacher, our rabbi, we helped families where the father would be away in labor camp that was attached to the army.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there-- these were poor families.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we bought food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we took to these poor families.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And looking back at it, I think I feel a little bit ashamed.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
